Tip of the Day

Materials

Materials are resource items that the player gathers from training the Agility, Foraging, Fishing, Mining, and Woodcutting skills. These items are then used in the Carpentry, Cooking, Crafting, Smithing, Trinketry skills to produce food, tools, weapons, shields, and jewelry. materials can also be received from chests.

Materials also have a fine version of themselves that can be be received in place of the regular version at a base rate of 1/100. These can be sold for a higher price to shops or allow better crafting quality chances.
